

	 
      Sang  shab ast o hava saaf,  mahtab bar labane berke boose mizanad,  man ,  eshghbazie anha ra be tamasha neshasteam,  bar takhte sangi ke hargez,  ashegh nemishavad.  shab ast o nasim,  ghasedak ha ra be manzel mibarad,  inja joz man o takhte sang kasi nist,  rahayam kon  bogzar dar berke fro ravam.    
    
